<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197913>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Male holotypes of (A, B) Limnonectes taylori (CUMZ (A) 7708 [former KUHE 19040]), and (C, D) L. jarujini (CUMZ (A) 7709 [= KUHE 20105]); dorsal (A, C) and ventral views (B, D). Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197913/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197914>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Toe web (A – C, ventral views) and tibia (D – F, dorsal views) of holotypes of (A, D) Limnonectes taylori and (B, E) L. jarujini, and (C, F) L. megastomias (THNHM 0 0 644 from Pang Sida National Park, Sa Kaeo Province). Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197914/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

